---
---

<section
  class="hero-section relative h-full overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10 px-6"
  aria-label="Josef Anolin — Stand-Up Comedian"
>
  <h1 class="sr-only">
    Josef Anolin — Stand-Up Comedian
  </h1>

  <div class="hero-comp">
    <img
      src="/joe-hero.png"
      alt=""
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="hero-portrait select-none pointer-events-none"
    />
    <img
      src="/joe-logo.png"
      alt="Josef Anolin — Stand Up Comedian"
      class="hero-logo select-none pointer-events-none"
    />
  </div>

  <p class="hero-bio">
    From Oakland, California currently living in Los Angeles, Josef has opened
    for the likes of Tom Segura, Whitney Cummings, and Michael Che. He likes
    telling irreverent stories based on his life and observations. He has an
    Android phone because he likes pissing you off with his green text bubbles.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    background: #000;
  }

  .hero-comp {
    position: relative;
    /* Cap width so height (= width / 1.6) leaves room for the bio + the
       hero card's 250px sticky-header clearance + gaps. */
    width: min(92%, 1100px, calc((100dvh - 420px) * 1.6));
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hero-portrait {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    right: 2%;
    width: 55%;
    height: auto;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-logo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 0%;
    width: 70%;
    height: auto;
    transform: translateY(-45%);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-bio {
    max-width: 56ch;
    text-align: center;
    color: rgb(229 229 229);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero-comp {
      width: 96%;
    }
    .hero-bio {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
</style>
